{"tid":2239853,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【打工仔喜訊】天文台明早日出前考慮改發八號信號","createTime":"2020-10-12T09:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T10:40:13.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7146e5a119c454bd2fba085a83e119c2c47e1a","tid":2239853,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"天文台在下午5時10分改發三號強風信號 。<br />\n<br />\n天文台會視乎本地風力情況，在明早日出前考慮改發八號烈風或暴風信號。<br />\n<br />\n在下午5時，熱帶風暴浪卡集結在香港之東南偏南約500公里，預料向西或西北偏西移動，時速約22公里，大致移向海南島一帶，並逐漸增強。<br />\n<br />\n按照現時預測路徑，浪卡會在今晚至明早最接近香港，在本港以南約500公里內掠過，再加上與一股東北季候風的共同影響，預料本港風勢會在晚間逐漸增強。與浪卡相關的狂風驟雨亦會逐漸影響廣東沿岸 。"},{"pid":"4836ea94d73cbb1969c34ce708cad031cf411bc9","tid":2239853,"uid":50502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"wfh<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553b909ddc82c019d654171e650722bc185f6eb1","tid":2239853,"uid":108757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"500km點會8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b31d31972116e842092041f89f876a40db788ee","tid":2239853,"uid":103362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"8號停工定wfh?"},{"pid":"c2a8d44b8139738b2f93e71ea1aa2de30c57ed72","tid":2239853,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441a3dfbb84f50a53789630d0e5ce2ca2a909010","tid":2239853,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"而家有wfh<